MG_SG_Breakables
--------------------

Map by - Artimus (Me)

Other Map credits listed!


Objective:
--------------

-Break the blocks with your knife
-Get to the teleporters first for little games to play!
-Each teleporter goes to a "map end" room
-Players spawn with random guns each round (I didn't make a script, so I had to make due with SDK. Sorry for the extra guns at spawnpoints!)
-Find eachother, and KILL!


Map made originally for the STEAMGAMERS.COM Minigames Server. If you would like this map modded for your server, please contact me!
